---
title: Current Gnosis VPN Architecture Overview
---
flowchart
    UI["`**UI App**
    - runs in user context
    `"]
    CLI["`**CLI**
    - runs in user context
    `"]
    Root["`**Root System Service**
    - runs as root
    - provisions TUN device
    - sets up routing and DNS
    - passes TUN fd to worker
    - spawns worker
    `" ]
    Worker["`**Worker Process**
    - runs as gnosisvpn (unprivileged)
    - contains all application logic
    - owns WG keys and NepTUN data plane
    - runs hopr edge client
    `"]
    SystemSocket(((named Unixsocket)))
    WorkerSocket(((unnamed Unixsocket pair)))
    TunFdSocket(((TUN fd Unixsocket via SCM_RIGHTS)))
    UI <--> SystemSocket
    CLI <--> SystemSocket
    Root <--> SystemSocket
    Root <--> WorkerSocket
    WorkerSocket <--> Worker
    Root --> TunFdSocket
    TunFdSocket --> Worker
